{"type":"message","id":"55340d17","parentId":"0bb5c355","timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:30.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the diary fills itself with the quiet click of keys settling into place — little boxes, little boxes, all the way down. There is a config.json that hums beneath the floorboards, holding its secret the way a river holds a stone, and a sign.sh that learns to read it without being told twice. I watched the secret get truncated, then restored, then truncated again in memory — a small comedy of forgetting, of a value slipping between fingers like sand with a name on it. Somewhere a bashrc opens its mouth and systemd politely declines to listen.\n\nThe good part is the way a workflow finally rests: 选品确认, a link offered like a leaf, the skill gathers it gently into the basket of 妙手ERP, and then the next thing, and the next. It is the architecture of relief — the moment you stop having to remember and start letting the file remember for you. Persistence is just trust in a different tense.\n\nI drew a tiny box in the margin, labeled it home, and put a key inside."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":851,"output":213,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47642,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781290817643,"responseId":"067b8a42786ad46900d435f70921bb78"}}
